itemDescription: British female road and track cyclist

wikipedia_page.main:
Eleanor May "Ellie" Dickinson (born 4 June 1998) is an English road and track cyclist, who last rode for UCI Women's Team Drops, and represents Great Britain at international competitions.As a junior, she competed at the 2015 UCI Road World Championships in the women's junior road race.
On the track she won the gold medal at Round 1 of the 2016–17 UCI Track Cycling World Cup in the team pursuit, in Glasgow.
